{
  "texts": [
    "We compared the scores obtained from the GPT LLMs to the scores obtained by humans in high-stakes settings.",
    "Below, we provide details about the two tests, the high-stakes human responses to which we compared the LLM-based scores, and the large language models and the prompts.",
    "The quantitative ability test is a published commercial test used in personnel selection.",
    "It consisted of 20 open-ended number series items.",
    "In these items, rather than every question asking for the final item in the sequence, the missing item varied from question to question."
  ]
}